#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The `quarkus-oidc-client` extension provides a reactive `io.quarkus.oidc.client.OidcClient`, which can be used to acquire and refresh tokens by using SmallRye Mutiny `Uni` and `Vert.x WebClient`."
msgstr "`quarkus-oidc-client` 扩展提供了一个响应式的 `io.quarkus.oidc.client.OidcClient，` 可用于通过 SmallRye Mutiny `Uni` 和 `Vert.x WebClient` 获取和刷新令牌。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"`OidcClient` is initialized at build time with the IDP token endpoint URL, which can be auto-discovered or manually configured.\n"
"`OidcClient` uses this endpoint to acquire access tokens with token grants such as `client_credentials` or `password`, and to refresh tokens with a `refresh_token` grant."
msgstr "`OidcClient` 在构建时会使用 IDP 令牌端点 URL 进行初始化，该 URL 可以自动发现，也可以手动配置。 `OidcClient` 使用该端点通过 `client_credentials` 或 `password` 等令牌授权方式获取访问令牌，并通过 `refresh_token` 授权方式刷新令牌。"

