#, fuzzy
msgid "The following sections show how `AccessTokenRequestFilter` and `JsonWebTokenRequestFilter` can help."
msgstr "以下各节将介绍 `AccessTokenRequestFilter` 和 `JsonWebTokenRequestFilter` 如何提供帮助。"

